     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT    DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION    SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.    MY-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.    MY-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT     SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT CADVEND ASSIGN TO DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT ARQ-SORT ASSIGN TO DISK.
    20     SELECT REL-PAG ASSIGN TO DISK
    21     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    22
    23 DATA    DIVISION.
    24 FILE    SECTION.
    25 FD CADVEND
    26     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    27     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADENT.DAT".
    28 01 REG-VEND.
    29     02 CODIDEP-ENT       PIC X(01).
    30     02 CODISEC-ENT       PIC X(01).
    31     02 CODIVEND-ENT      PIC 9(05).
    32     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    33     02 VALVENDAS-ENT     PIC 9(07)V99.
    34     02 SALFIXO-ENT       PIC 9(07)V99.
    35     02 DESC-ENT          PIC 9(05)V99.
    36 SD ARQ-SORT.
    37 01 REG-SORT.
    38     02 CODIDEP-SORT       PIC X(01).
    39     02 CODISEC-SORT       PIC X(01).
    40     02 CODIVEND-SORT      PIC 9(05).
    41     02 NOME-SORT          PIC X(20).
    42     02 VALVENDAS-SORT     PIC 9(07)V99.
    43     02 SALFIXO-SORT       PIC 9(07)V99.
    44     02 DESC-SORT          PIC 9(05)V99.
    45 FD REL-PAG
    46     LABEL RECORD  OMITTED.
    47 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(130).
    48 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    49     77 FIM-ARQ-ENTRADA  PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    50     77 FIM-ARQ-SAIDA    PIC X(03) VALUE "NAO".
    51     77 CT-LIN           PIC 9(02) VALUE 41.
    52     77 CT-PAG           PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    53     77 COMISSAO         PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    54     77 SALBRUTO         PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    55     77 SALLIQUIDO       PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    56     77 SOMA-SEC         PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
    57     77 SOMA-DEP         PIC 9(10)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 19:56 Page   2
*                                      EXERC6.CBL
    58     77 SEC              PIC X(01).
    59     77 DEP              PIC X(01).
    60
    61 01 WHITE-CAB.
    62     02 FILLER     PIC X(130) VALUE SPACES.
    63 01 CAB-01.
    64     02 FILLER     PIC X(45) VALUE SPACES.
    65     02 FILLER     PIC X(22) VALUE "RELATÓRIO DE PAGAMENTO".
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    67     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    68     02 VAR-PAG    PIC ZZ9.
    69 01 CAB-DEP.
    70     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE "DEPARTAMENTO = ".
    71     02 VAR-DEP PIC X(01).
    72 01 CAB-SEC.
    73     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE "SEÇĂO        = ".
    74     02 VAR-SEC    PIC X(01).
    75 01 CAB-02.
    76     02 FILLER     PIC X(06) VALUE "CÓDIGO".
    77     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
    78     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE "NOME".
    79     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
    80     02 FILLER     PIC X(09) VALUE "SAL. FIXO".
    81     02 FILLER     PIC X(12) VALUE SPACES.
    82     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "COMISSĂO".
    83     02 FILLER     PIC X(12) VALUE SPACES.
    84     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE "SAL. BRUTO".
    85     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE SPACES.
    86     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "DESCONTO".
    87     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    88     02 FILLER     PIC X(12) VALUE "SAL. LÍQUIDO".
    89 01 DETALHE.
    90     02 FILLER        PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
    91     02 VAR-COD       PIC ZZZZ9.
    92     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    93     02 VAR-NOME      PIC X(20) .
    94     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    95     02 VAR-FIXO      PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
    96     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    97     02 VAR-COMISSAO  PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
    98     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
    99     02 VAR-BRUTO     PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
   100     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
   101     02 VAR-DESCONTO  PIC ZZ.ZZ9,99.
   102     02 FILLER        PIC X(5) VALUE SPACES.
   103     02 VAR-LIQUIDO   PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
   104
   105 01 RODAPE-SEC.
   106     02 FILLER     PIC X(28) VALUE "TOTAL DE SALÁRIOS DA SEÇĂO: ".
   107     02 ROD-SEC  PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
   108 01 RODAPE-DEP.
   109     02 FILLER     PIC X(35)
   110         VALUE "TOTAL DE SALÁRIOS DO DEPARTAMENTO: ".
   111     02 ROD-DEP  PIC Z.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99.
   112 PROCEDURE    DIVISION.
   113 PGM-EX05.
   114 SORT    ARQ-SORT
   115         ON ASCENDING KEY CODIDEP-SORT
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 19:56 Page   3
*                                      EXERC6.CBL
   116         ON ASCENDING KEY CODISEC-SORT
   117         USING CADVEND
   118         OUTPUT PROCEDURE ROT-RELATORIO.
   119 STOP    RUN.
   120
   121 ROT-RELATORIO SECTION.
   122     PERFORM INICIO-SAIDA.
   123     PERFORM PRINCIPAL-SAIDA
   124             UNTIL FIM-ARQ-SAIDA EQUAL "SIM".
   125     PERFORM FIM-SAIDA.
   126
   127 INICIO-SAIDA SECTION.
   128     OPEN OUTPUT REL-PAG.
   129     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   130
   131 LEITURA-SAIDA SECTION.
   132     RETURN ARQ-SORT INTO REG-SORT
   133      AT END
   134      PERFORM RODAPE
   135      MOVE 'SIM' TO FIM-ARQ-SAIDA.
   136
   137 PRINCIPAL-SAIDA SECTION.
   138     PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA.
   139     PERFORM LEITURA-SAIDA.
   140
   141 GRAVACAO-SAIDA SECTION.
   142     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 40
   143         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   144     END-IF.
   145     IF NOT(CODIDEP-SORT = DEP)
   146          PERFORM CABECALHO-02
   147     ELSE IF NOT(CODISEC-SORT = SEC)
   148          PERFORM CABECALHO-03
   149     END-IF.
   150     MOVE CODIDEP-SORT TO DEP.
   151     MOVE CODISEC-SORT TO SEC.
   152     PERFORM DETALHES.
   153 CABECALHO-01   SECTION.
   154     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   155     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   156     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   157     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
   158     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   159     WRITE REG-ATR FROM WHITE-CAB AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   160     MOVE 2  TO CT-LIN.
   161 CABECALHO-02 SECTION.
   162     MOVE CODISEC-SORT TO VAR-SEC.
   163     IF NOT(SOMA-SEC = ZEROS) AND NOT(SOMA-DEP = ZEROS)
   164         ADD SOMA-SEC TO SOMA-DEP
   165         MOVE SOMA-SEC TO ROD-SEC
   166         MOVE SOMA-DEP TO ROD-DEP
   167         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   168         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-DEP AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   169         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   170         MOVE ZEROS TO SOMA-DEP
   171         MOVE ZEROS TO SOMA-SEC
   172     END-IF.
   173     MOVE CODIDEP-SORT TO VAR-DEP.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 26-May-25 19:56 Page   4
*                                      EXERC6.CBL
   174     IF CT-LIN = 2
   175         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-DEP AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   176          ADD 4        TO CT-LIN
   177     ELSE
   178         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-DEP AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   179          ADD 5        TO CT-LIN
   180     END-IF.
   181     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   182     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   183 CABECALHO-03 SECTION.
   184     MOVE CODISEC-SORT TO VAR-SEC.
   185     MOVE SOMA-SEC TO ROD-SEC.
   186     ADD SOMA-SEC TO SOMA-DEP.
   187     IF CT-LIN = 2
   188        WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   189         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   190          ADD 3        TO CT-LIN
   191     ELSE
   192         WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   193         WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE
   194          ADD 4        TO CT-LIN
   195     END-IF.
   196     MOVE ZEROS TO SOMA-SEC
   197     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   198 DETALHES SECTION.
   199     IF VALVENDAS-SORT <= 1000
   200         COMPUTE COMISSAO = VALVENDAS-SORT * (5/100)
   201     ELSE IF VALVENDAS-SORT <= 3000
   202         COMPUTE COMISSAO = VALVENDAS-SORT * (10/100)
   203     ELSE
   204         COMPUTE COMISSAO = VALVENDAS-SORT * (15/100)
   205     END-IF.
   206     COMPUTE SALBRUTO = SALFIXO-SORT + COMISSAO.
   207     COMPUTE SALLIQUIDO = SALBRUTO - DESC-SORT.
   208     MOVE CODIVEND-SORT TO VAR-COD.
   209     MOVE NOME-SORT TO VAR-NOME.
   210     MOVE SALFIXO-SORT TO VAR-FIXO.
   211     MOVE COMISSAO TO VAR-COMISSAO.
   212     MOVE SALBRUTO TO VAR-BRUTO.
   213     MOVE DESC-SORT TO VAR-DESCONTO.
   214     MOVE SALLIQUIDO TO VAR-LIQUIDO.
   215     WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE.
   216     ADD SALLIQUIDO TO SOMA-SEC.
   217
   218
   219 RODAPE SECTION.
   220     MOVE SOMA-SEC TO ROD-SEC.
   221     MOVE SOMA-DEP TO ROD-DEP.
   222     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-SEC AFTER ADVANCING 2 LINE.
   223     WRITE REG-ATR FROM RODAPE-DEP AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   224
   225 FIM-SAIDA SECTION.
   226     CLOSE REL-PAG.
